Repr.mutate also calls _FlushRepr after executing the function mutating the inner field.
_FlushRepr:{#[T](Repr[T]):Void->Magic!}//flushes ReprAux.IdentityHashmap.get(repr)
.cacheLook(f:NonCaptureRF[T,R]):R->f._get(this);
NonCaptureRF[T,A,R]:NonCapture[NonCaptureRF[T,A,R]]{
